name: Re/Max Community Realty
overview:
RE/MAX Community Realty has been serving Whittier and surrounding areas for over 15 years. Take a look at the complete list of areas we service here.

Our agents have an average 15 years of real estate experience. Tenacious yet flexible in negotiations and responsive to their clients, we will make sure all your questions and concerns are answered. You can meet our agents here.

RE/MAX Community Realty has been awarded the Rating of “Very High Customer Satisfaction”.

There are a lot of ways to judge a company, but the best indicator is customer satisfaction. Think about it. A painter may have a nice portfolio but dissatisfies his customers because of job tardiness. A company with a high level of customer satisfaction is a company likely to excel in every aspect of their business.

Value Star’s Customer Satisfaction Ratings So, the best way to discover which companies are the best, is to talk to their customers. And, not just 2 or 3, but 100. That’s how Value Star performs its ratings. Value Star makes certain it selects a large random sample of customers. Then, the customers are scientifically surveyed with university audit control to ensure accuracy and objectiveness Only the Best Companies Earn Value Star Certified. Only when a company is found to have a very high customer satisfaction rating does it earn the privilege of displaying the Value Star Certified symbol for one year. You’re the customer, and you need to make the decision. Before you choose, make certain they’re Value Star” Certified.
